<paragraph id="8EC7F06FBF0AC056B4F6B9A02DEBABF0" pageId="null" pageNumber="602">
Pflanze 
<normalizedToken id="E1D2EAA1793FA1A9B86EC574A20C78BB" originalValue="±" pageId="null" pageNumber="602">+/-</normalizedToken>
kahl. 
<emphasis id="E30A44EAF6CD9A33321EE98F5B8F4AF0" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="602">
Kelch 6-10 mm lang; 
<normalizedToken id="294AF5C2B99429D59FA3A8907AB02C01" originalValue="längere" pageId="null" pageNumber="602">laengere</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="678F2EF43645337B9AB7798C30413E9D" originalValue="Kelchzähne" pageId="null" pageNumber="602">Kelchzaehne</normalizedToken>
1-1
</emphasis>
⅓ 
<emphasis id="CB7FEBE772D38B689664D87AAAD9D270" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="602">
so lang wie die 
<normalizedToken id="A5A1FB7C62ADA568703615503050BD85" originalValue="Kelchröhre" pageId="null" pageNumber="602">Kelchroehre</normalizedToken>
. Krone 1,3-1,8 cm lang.
</emphasis>
Frucht 3-4 cm lang und 0,5-0,7 cm breit. - 
<normalizedToken id="C58675502FFC9A847815ADD80C42BC35" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="602">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="4F45E4918E6B424160E9BC827DDC20A4" pageId="null" pageNumber="602">
<emphasis id="52F6D4C8891DE79603484CA838276B1E" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="602">Zytologische Angaben. 2n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="1A0ED733FADF35FCFAB13315598A7CF8" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="602">28:</emphasis>
Material aus Hospental, Champex und Kleiner St. Bernhard (Brunsberg 1965, als 
<taxonomicName id="F1D9899404C75763ED315FCBF846F7AA" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fabaceae" genus="Lathyrus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fabales" pageId="null" pageNumber="602" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="pratensis">
